{
  "name": "Pinterest WF3 - Verify Published",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Pinterest – Workflow 3: Verify published pins\n\nReads rows where **Status = Scheduled** (with a Tailwind Post ID) from **both** the **Pinterest Pins** tab (blog-sourced) and the **Pinterest2:3 Pins** tab (product-photo-sourced), calls Tailwind **Get Post**, and when the post is **published** (status = sent), writes the real **Pinterest URL** into **Pin URL** and sets **Status = Published** + actual **Pinned Time** back to whichever tab that row came from (tracked internally as `_sourceTab`).\n\n**Setup:** Google Sheets + Tailwind (Bearer) credentials; accountId, pinsTab, and pinsTab2 in Set Config.",
        "height": 476,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "f655c399-06d4-460a-909f-615906a6a447",
      "name": "README",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        832,
        -16
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "triggerAtMinute": 5
            }
          ]
        }
      },
